Module com.cab302.wellbeing.model
Package com.cab302.wellbeing.controller

Class UserProfileController

java.lang.Object
com.cab302.wellbeing.controller.UserProfileController
public class UserProfileController extends Object
This class is a controller for the User Profile functionality in the application. It provides methods to handle the user profile (name, email, password, etc.) of the application.
